headline: Ex-NCAA Prez Emmert Unloads Shares of Logistics Firm Expeditors
summary: Mark Emmert, the former NCAA president, recently sold 4,100 shares of Expeditors International, a Bellevue, Wash.-based company where he has served on the board of directors since 2008.
